Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Used to add to an entity's list of targets.

Usage
-----

*float* appendTarget( *entity* **target** )

Parameters
----------

-   [target] - Entity to be targetted.

Examples
--------

    $my_entity.appendTarget( $my_entity2 );

Notes
-----

Not available.


